t\nmultiple scattering in optically thin polar outflows is the mechanism that\ngives high DoP in post-AGB stars with a bipolar or multi-polar envelopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2017 19:36:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
